      "id": "1d965076aa09efe4",
      "text": "In the criticism of aesthetics, the [[Evidence and Corroboration]] in the four [[Relatively Adequate Hypotheses]] detailed in [[World Hypotheses: A Study in Evidence (1942)]] provides some insight into metaphysical stances that can be taken."
